(i)  Generate a token.
(ii) Hit the product offer search api .....v1/search/combined(For fetching the document_id from the response) and 
     fetch the documentId.
     Inside documents --> documentMetadata --> documentId.

(iii) Hit the product offer json fetch api .....v1/search/related/ids passing the documentId in the id of ids array in 
product offer json fetch request.
   Request    
"ids" :[{
                "id" : "documentId"
             }]

